data.title: The 44th Annual Miss USA Pageant (TV Special 1995)
data.meta_description: The 44th Annual Miss USA Pageant: With Chris Arpad, Jennifer Aubin, Deana Avila, Kristen Bettis. 50 contestants, representing each state in America, vie to become the 44th Miss USA. Held at South Padre Island, Texas culminating in the final competition and crowning on February 10, 1995. Chelsi Smith of Texas was crowned.
